description:
🥁 Bristolian MLOps Community 🥁

📅 Save the date

Looking forward to our next Bristol Meetup?

Our friends from [Berkeley Square](https://bsqtalent.com/) will be hosting us on the 26th of March for an exciting meetup.

Agenda for the day:

**18:00** \- 🍕🍺 Welcome 🍕🍺

**18:25** \- MLOps\.Community Intro

**18:30** \- "Under the hood of an algorithmic hedge fund" by [Pierre Cilliers](https://www.linkedin.com/in/pierre-cilliers-4b778b162/) from [Spatialedge](https://www.linkedin.com/company/spatialedge/)
**19:15** \- "Synthetic data for machine learning" by [Rich Riley](https://www.linkedin.com/in/rich-j-riley/) from [Rowden](https://www.linkedin.com/company/rowden/)
**20:00 -** Start heading to the pub

This meetup is sponsored by [Berkeley Square](https://bsqtalent.com) 🙏 🍻 🍕
title: MLOps Bristol - Meetup #11
